test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -1681 == -41
 +  where -1681 = <built-in function prod>([-41, -1, -41])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x73e42a297400>([-41])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x73e42a297400> = [[1, -41], [1, -41, 1], [-41, 1], [-41, 1, -41], [1, -41], [1, -41, 1], ...].count
